16:12.239 --> 16:13.000
Where's the money going?

16:13.020 --> 16:13.581
What's happening?

16:14.522 --> 16:22.151
It's those little $10 decisions compounded over time where if you don't stop and you look back and evaluate, then you're never going to understand what's happening with your life.

16:23.433 --> 16:26.277
