16:26.857 --> 16:33.586
So maybe you're the type that's drinking a little too much and you don't realize that if you keep drinking, you're going to lose your family because they're going to bail because they're not going to put up with it.

16:34.114 --> 16:41.463
Or maybe you keep taking pills, you keep smoking, you keep doing whatever you're doing, you're not gonna be able to hold down a job because you'll keep failing drug test after drug test.

16:42.244 --> 16:45.789
You keep talking your spouse the way that you're talking to and they're gonna be able because they're not gonna stand for that.

16:46.389 --> 16:53.819
