17:29.730 --> 17:30.751
Why don't I have an eight pack?

17:30.771 --> 17:33.215
Well, it's because you're on 19 hours a day to work out and eat clean.

17:33.715 --> 17:34.517
Like, that's reality.

17:35.217 --> 17:38.041
Compare yourself to who you are and who God is calling you to be.

17:38.101 --> 17:42.087
Your time, your resources, your abilities, your potential.

17:42.608 --> 17:43.849
Don't put so much pressure on yourself.

17:43.869 --> 17:48.456
