18:11.607 --> 18:18.419
In some translation, it says it is God-breathed and is useful to teach us what is true and to make us realize what is wrong in our lives.

18:18.439 --> 18:22.866
So if you're looking for a little direction, you're looking for reproved correction and training, this is a good spot to go.

18:23.554 --> 18:27.099
