And the man answered, you must love the Lord your God with all your heart, all your soul, all your mind, all your strength and love your neighbor as yourself.

19:33.771 --> 19:34.792
We have heard that before.

19:34.833 --> 19:37.416
If you're new, those will be the most important commandments.

19:38.237 --> 19:41.722
Right, Jesus told him, do this and you will live.

