21:01.022 --> 21:01.864
He takes him to the inn.

21:02.164 --> 21:04.269
In the next town, he puts him up in bed.

21:04.510 --> 21:05.512
And he doesn't just leave him.

21:05.552 --> 21:06.514
He cares for him.

21:07.330 --> 21:12.355
And when it's time for him to go, he goes down to the innkeeper and he slides two pieces of silver across the desk.

21:12.375 --> 21:19.743
And he says, if the cost to take care of this man exceeds these two pieces of silver, you put it on my tab, I'll pay it, I'm good for it the next time I'm around.

21:20.865 --> 21:28.813
So Jesus tells the guy this story and he says, now, based on that, based on those three people who pass this person by, the person on the ground, who was the neighbor?

21:29.994 --> 21:33.979
And the expert of religious law says, the one who showed that man mercy.

21:34.699 --> 21:37.202
And Jesus, the expert, the master of the mic drop,

21:37.538 --> 21:42.364
Said this, yes, now go and do the same.

21:43.586 --> 21:54.059
So you wanna use this as a way to evaluate your life, the decisions you're making, the measuring stick you should be using for how to live, how to treat people, how to love, how to love God, how to love others, how to serve them.

21:54.099 --> 21:58.245
Don't compare yourself to Instagram, compare yourself to this standard.

21:58.725 --> 22:01.729
Cause it's all right here and you can dive in it anytime you like.

22:02.290 --> 22:03.511
That's part of the evaluation.

22:04.012 --> 22:05.554
And if we don't evaluate,

22:06.114 --> 22:08.998
Throughout this process, if we don't evaluate the last in life, here's what can happen.

22:09.039 --> 22:13.626
Mark Twain said it this way, the best predictor of future behavior is past behavior.

22:14.487 --> 22:17.632
So we are doomed to repeat the mistakes of our past if we do not get this right.

22:18.193 --> 22:23.241
Psalms 119, it says, I ponder the direction of my life and I turn to follow your laws.

22:23.922 --> 22:31.794
So as you're thinking, as you're evaluating, as you're pondering the direction of your life, we talk about the turn all the time that repentance turn and turn to follow Christ.

22:32.162 --> 22:33.544
So I'm trying to follow the ways of the world.

22:33.564 --> 22:34.506
