24:16.012 --> 24:16.993
I'm trying to not die.

24:17.273 --> 24:18.154
That would be the purpose for that.

24:20.237 --> 24:22.239
And it's kind of morbid to think about, but I've got a wife.

24:22.660 --> 24:23.901
