31:06.146 --> 31:22.908
But if you do not commit to the Lord, whatever you do and allow Him to establish your plans, if you don't commit to allow Him to glorify Him for the next 10 years, to truly connect with Him and allow Him to guide your path and allow Him to guide your steps, man, it's all going to feel hollow.

31:24.250 --> 31:25.391
